<p>
This package provides a portable abstraction around the various
dynamic library/symbol loading interfaces on various platforms.
</p>
<p>
It currently provides a uniform interface around:
</p>
<p>
<ul>
  <li><span><span class="package">dlfcn</span> - <span class="c_function">dlopen()</span>, <span class="c_function">dlsym()</span> on POSIX platforms.</span></li>
  <li><span><span class="c_function">LoadLibrary()</span>, <span class="c_function">GetProcAddress()</span> on Windows.</span></li>
</ul>
</p>
